      <title>杰富瑞的前海豹突击队在不良债务投资方面取得优势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/jefferies-ex-navy-seal-gains-edge-in-distressed-debt-investing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在杰富瑞金融集团公司（Jefferies Financial Group Inc.），由前海豹突击队员领导的一小群交易员和分析师在拥挤且充满争议的不良债务世界中发挥着巨大的影响力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/jefferies-ex-navy-seal-gains-edge-in-distressed-debt-investing</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
