    <item>
      <title>埃及、巴基斯坦等待新兴市场降级威胁的判决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/egypt-pakistan-await-verdict-on-emerging-market-demotion-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及和巴基斯坦面临失去新兴市场地位的威胁，这两个国家将于周三了解其经济复苏计划是否足以避免在富时罗素指数中被降级。越南正在等待一次难以捉摸的晋升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/egypt-pakistan-await-verdict-on-emerging-market-demotion-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 12:09:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度将在选举前减少债券发行量并纳入指数</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/india-plans-90-billion-of-bond-sales-in-fiscal-first-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于政策制定者在选举前控制支出并将该国债务纳入全球指数，印度发行的债券将少于预期。]]></description>
