      <title>日元跌至 1990 年以来最低水平，日本加大干预威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yen-drops-to-lowest-since-1990-amid-intervention-speculation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日元兑美元汇率跌至约 34 年来的最低水平后，日本就其干预货币市场的意愿向交易员发出了迄今为止最严厉的警告。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/yen-drops-to-lowest-since-1990-amid-intervention-speculation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 02:54:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员关注日元水平，标普 500 指数期货上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员为季末再平衡做准备，美国股指期货小幅走高。由于市场猜测日本官员可能准备进行干预以支撑日元汇率，日元从 34 年来的低点反弹。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
